1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,520
Welcome to ARCANE OS.

2
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:05,540
ARCANE stands for Adaptive Runtime for
Cognitive AI Native Environments.

3
00:00:05,780 --> 00:00:10,220
It is an AI-native operating environment designed
around what a person is trying to accomplish,

4
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:13,800
not around finding the right app, file,
or sequence of menus.

5
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:18,800
Under ARCANE, intent, context, memory, policy,
and capabilities work together.

6
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:20,040
You express a goal.

7
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:24,760
ARCANE helps assemble the approved tools and
information needed to move that goal forward,

8
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:29,700
while keeping important actions visible and governed
by the permissions of the person and the device.

9
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:32,680
ARCANE is not a chatbot pasted onto a desktop.

10
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:36,980
It is the environment through which people and
intelligent systems work with the computer.

11
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:42,160
The familiar shell, settings, documents, and
specialized applications remain available,

12
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:45,540
but they are connected through a shared runtime
and capability boundary.

13
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:50,140
ARCANE currently runs on both Microsoft NT
and the Linux kernel.

14
00:00:50,340 --> 00:00:55,320
That makes it adaptable to the controls of a regulated
workplace and to the needs of a personal device.

15
00:00:55,500 --> 00:01:00,860
The underlying platform supplies drivers, identity,
processes, and hardware access.

16
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:05,000
ARCANE supplies the consistent experience
and governed collaboration layer.

17
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,600
Android support is currently under development.

18
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:12,940
The result is one environment that can serve engineers,
operators, families, security teams,

19
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:17,580
and mission-focused organizations without asking
every user to become a systems expert.

20
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:19,880
ARCANE asks a different question.

21
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:22,620
How should humans and intelligent systems
work together?

22
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:27,460
Explore the shell, open an application, and begin
with the outcome you want to achieve.

23
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,880
Welcome to ARCANE.

